ike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T15:52:23.000Z","msg":"我成日都單機係茶記食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我後生仔加有女都要咁慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c27fc0c7428a2d025af6646197ed4c7c4c2859a","tid":29461,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T16:03:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同呀爸分開住好多年<br />\n一個月見一次<br />\n想像到佢成日自己一個食飯都有d 心up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多d睇你阿爸<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6c2ae3ce088a6f0fb14e062184252a47b5ec94d","tid":29461,"uid":23878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T16:04:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一個人食飯有乜問題？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾撚時有人話過有問題呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc3a3faa344055e4c9d0282c468ed6a47be58fe0","tid":29461,"uid":16085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T16:16:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似每個麻甩佬都有自己既故事<br />\n有d可能幾十歲仲單身<br />\n有d可能食完仲要開工<br />\n有d可能啱啱先放工<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你第一句好似我呢排同朋友，因為我見過既經歷，曾經講過既說話<br />\n<br />\n有次放工搭巴士，附近有一男一女，個女係咁喊，細細聲哭泣，男既就係度安慰佢。<br />\n<br />\n同一日，行到樓下附近見到兩個學生哥，其中一個好激動係度喊，又踢牆又盛。偷偷地比左包紙巾佢地就走左。<br />\n<br />\n每個人都有自己既故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能分手<br />\n可能屋企人有事<br />\n可能自己有事<br />\n可能乜乜乜<br />\n<br />\n人大左，慢慢會明點解公園咁多叔叔伯伯有屋企唔番，一個人係度「偶」臭。慢慢發覺自己有時想整支煙仔食下，唔如意既事有好多，有幾分鐘比自己停下，係一種過渡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}